Summary: Two star-like objects traveling west to east
divs: Sighting DetailsOn Tuesday night September 8, 2009 at around 2215 local time while taking a walk I observed two star-like objects traveling across the sky.These two objects, one following the other, came from the west near the big dipper to my north, traveled in an easterly direction for about two minutes then turned slightly northwest before disappearing as they faded out. This was my second sighting in a year and my third sighting in my life. I find them to be very interesting and after noticing these latest objects I hope to see them again.
